1) Program to find maximum and minimum number from command-line arguments
class Test {    public static void main(String[] args) {        int max = Integer.parseInt(args[0]);        int min = Integer.parseInt(args[0]);        for(int i=1; i<args.length; i++) {            int num = Integer.parseInt(args[i]);            if(num > max)                max = num;            if(num < min)                min = num;        }        System.out.println("Max = " + max);        System.out.println("Min = " + min);    }}

Execution
java Test 10 50 5 80 20

Output
Max = 80Min = 5

